Parameters:
mediaItemThe media item owner
effectIdThe effect id
startTimeMsThe start time relative to the media item to which it is applied
durationMsThe duration of this effect in milliseconds
typetype of the effect. type is one of: TYPE_COLOR, TYPE_GRADIENT, TYPE_SEPIA, TYPE_NEGATIVE, TYPE_FIFTIES.
colorIf type is TYPE_COLOR, color is the RGB color as 888. If type is TYPE_GRADIENT, color is the RGB color at the top of the frame. Otherwise, color is ignored
